parallel to one another...

465
00:43:56,099 --> 00:43:58,897
and also perpendicular
to the picture plane,

466
00:43:59,102 --> 00:44:04,096
the projection thus forming a plane
is called orthographic projection.

467
00:44:04,508 --> 00:44:08,035
When a surface, front, side or top...

468
00:44:08,512 --> 00:44:11,037
of the object is to
be depicted separately,

469
00:44:11,114 --> 00:44:13,844
it is drawn in the
true shape and proportion,

