I didn't want to send him to the hospital.
I said it was a mistake.

1137
01:42:51,564 --> 01:42:54,362
I didn't want to hit him.
I apologized to him.

1138
01:42:54,434 --> 01:42:59,098
Well done, Sir.
Scar the child for life, scare him to death...

1139
01:42:59,439 --> 01:43:02,374
And then apologise.
Your father would have been proud.

1140
01:43:04,778 --> 01:43:08,771
I said it happened by mistake,
I didn't want to hit him...

1141
01:43:09,382 --> 01:43:10,440
Did I tell you?

1142
01:43:12,185 --> 01:43:13,243
Sir?

1143
01:43:13,386 --> 01:43:14,444
What?

1144
01:43:14,854 --> 01:43:16,446
Won't you apologise to me now?

1145
01:43:16,790 --> 01:43:17,848
You!

1146
01:44:35,335 --> 01:44:36,393
Good morning.

1147
01:44:37,470 --> 01:44:38,528
Good morning, Sir.

1148
01:44:40,607 --> 01:44:41,869
Arjun get up.

1149
01:44:43,877 --> 01:44:45,344
I know you're awake.

1150
