then there's the two of you.

1154
01:45:05,565 --> 01:45:06,964
I get frustrated.

1155
01:45:08,568 --> 01:45:10,433
I get angry, and then...

1156
01:45:14,440 --> 01:45:15,907
I thought a lot last night.

1157
01:45:19,379 --> 01:45:21,244
I have done a lot for both of you.

1158
01:45:22,982 --> 01:45:25,917
But it was never enough.

1159
01:45:26,986 --> 01:45:28,248
And it never will be.

1160
01:45:31,257 --> 01:45:34,124
Rohan, since you don't want to study,

1161
01:45:34,994 --> 01:45:37,929
there's no need to study any more.

1162
01:45:39,332 --> 01:45:42,529
You start work full-time
at the factory today.

1163
01:45:43,536 --> 01:45:45,936
You will reach one hour
earlier before the others...

1164
01:45:47,006 --> 01:45:50,999
and you leave two hours
after they leave. Okay?

1165
01:45:53,012 --> 01:45:54,070
Arjun.

1166
01:45:55,014 --> 01:45:56,538
I have spoken to the principal.

1167
01:45:57,684 --> 01:45:59,675
A new semester starts in two weeks.

1168
01:46:00,687 --> 01:46:04,882
You're going to boarding school.
To study and live there.

1169
01:46:06,225 --> 01:46:07,283
Okay?

1170
01:46:14,634 --> 01:46:17,694
I've decided to marry again.
For myself.

1171
01:46:20,039 --> 01:46:21,301
I get very lonely.

1172
01:46:22,709 --> 01:46:26,110
