I will always be their enemy.

1181
01:47:01,547 --> 01:47:03,742
But they're your children.

1182
01:47:04,017 --> 01:47:05,484
You're sending Arjun
to boarding school?

1183
01:47:05,551 --> 01:47:06,609
He's only six years old...

1184
01:47:06,686 --> 01:47:09,018
I was six when dad sent me...

1185
01:47:09,422 --> 01:47:11,287
But Arjun isn't like you.

1186
01:47:11,758 --> 01:47:14,488
Then he'll become like me.
Forget all this...

1187
01:47:15,161 --> 01:47:17,356
You want a drink?

1188
01:47:18,031 --> 01:47:19,089
No.

1189
01:47:24,437 --> 01:47:27,031
Please think about what you're doing.

1190
01:47:27,240 --> 01:47:28,571
I have thought about it...

1191
01:47:29,709 --> 01:47:31,233
I took this decision after thinking.

1192
01:47:33,780 --> 01:47:37,716
If it's too much for you,
we can take care of Arjun.

1193
01:47:41,788 --> 01:47:43,050
What did you say?

1194
01:47:48,194 --> 01:47:49,252
What do you mean by too much?

1195
01:47:49,662 --> 01:47:51,061
I mean...

1196
01:47:51,130 --> 01:47:53,257
What do you mean by too much?

1197
01:47:53,800 --> 01:47:57,463
We can bring him up.
Take care of him. Send him to school.

1198
01:47:57,737 --> 01:47:59,466
- We have no children...
- Arjun is my son.

1199
01:48:00,139 --> 01:48:02,073
And I'm not in the
business of selling children.

1200
01:48:02,141 --> 01:48:03,472
Why take this the wrong way?

1201
01:48:03,543 --> 01:48:06,410
- All I'm saying is, if it's too hard...
- What are you saying?

1202
01:48:06,479 --> 01:48:09,073
It isn't my fault that
you didn't have children.

1203
01:48:09,148 --> 01:48:12,481
