1206
01:48:16,556 --> 01:48:17,818
You want to tell me what's fair?

1207
01:48:19,826 --> 01:48:21,157
Get lost...

1208
01:48:24,430 --> 01:48:26,159
What is your problem?

1209
01:48:28,101 --> 01:48:30,433
Why can't you ever see anyone happy?

1210
01:48:30,503 --> 01:48:31,561
I'm tired.

1211
01:48:32,238 --> 01:48:34,103
I'm tired of making everyone happy!

1212
