First Father, then you!
Now these two! I can't take it!

1213
01:48:36,776 --> 01:48:39,643
- Have you ever given him one chance?
- One chance?

1214
01:48:40,379 --> 01:48:43,314
I put everything into his education!
He got kicked out!

1215
01:48:43,382 --> 01:48:46,112
I begged for his admission into College!
He failed!

1216
01:48:46,185 --> 01:48:47,243
What else has he ever done?

1217
01:48:47,320 --> 01:48:49,720
- He's written a novel.
- He's written shit!

1218
01:48:50,323 --> 01:48:51,847
Stop encouraging him!

1219
01:48:52,525 --> 01:48:55,585
Stop living your
unfulfilled dreams through my son!

1220
01:48:56,529 --> 01:48:58,190
I don't want him to become like you!

1221
01:48:58,598 --> 01:48:59,656
Like me?

1222
01:48:59,799 --> 01:49:02,131
Look at yourself...!

1223
01:49:02,869 --> 01:49:05,804
Big fat bloody loser.

1224
01:49:08,341 --> 01:49:11,674
What are you looking at? Get out!

1225
01:49:31,898 --> 01:49:33,160
Uncle.

1226
