- Take me with you.
- No, no, no, no...

1228
01:49:37,570 --> 01:49:39,231
- Please Uncle.
- You have to stay here.

1229
01:49:39,305 --> 01:49:40,636
Arjun needs you.

1230
01:49:40,706 --> 01:49:41,832
He's going to boarding school.

1231
01:49:41,908 --> 01:49:44,775
He'll need you when he gets back.

1232
01:49:45,444 --> 01:49:46,843
You're his only friend.

1233
01:49:46,913 --> 01:49:49,245
- Please Uncle.
- Come on Rohan.

1234
01:49:49,315 --> 01:49:50,646
Don't do this to me right now.

1235
01:49:50,716 --> 01:49:54,311
- Please Uncle. Please Uncle...
- Don't do this to me. Don't do this to me right now.

1236
01:49:55,188 --> 01:49:56,246
Uncle!

1237
01:50:15,942 --> 01:50:17,807
No Papa... No Papa...

1238
01:50:18,411 --> 01:50:21,278
Papa no. Please...
Papa no. Please...

1239
01:50:21,547 --> 01:50:23,674
Sir, please no...

1240
01:50:52,578 --> 01:51:03,921
Against the rising waves your
boat is helpless and tired.

1241
01:51:03,990 --> 01:51:14,992
Living one gasp at a time...
Your boat is helpless and tired.

1242
01:51:15,534 --> 01:51:26,001
Though the currents are against you...

