Fly and reach for the sun...

1251
01:52:32,912 --> 01:52:41,081
Leave behind the darkness.

1252
01:52:44,557 --> 01:52:46,354
This is my son Rohan.

1253
01:52:46,492 --> 01:52:48,551
Rohan, this is Madhavi.

1254
01:52:48,828 --> 01:52:50,489
Hi Rohan. It's nice to meet you.

1255
01:52:50,763 --> 01:52:51,821
Hello.

1256
01:52:52,631 --> 01:52:54,030
And this is her daughter Richa.

1257
01:52:54,100 --> 01:52:55,761
Richa, say hello...

1258
01:52:55,901 --> 01:52:56,959
Hello.

1259
01:52:59,772 --> 01:53:01,103
Go wash up.

1260
01:53:01,907 --> 01:53:02,965
Come on.

1261
01:53:09,582 --> 01:53:21,392
Powerful storms will shake you...

1262
