If you surrender to a whirIpool...

1263
01:53:26,599 --> 01:53:32,663
What good is your might?

1264
01:53:32,738 --> 01:53:35,571
Let the light
in your heart overcome

1265
01:53:35,641 --> 01:53:38,405
Break away from the night...

1266
01:53:38,477 --> 01:53:43,574
Master the tides...

1267
01:53:44,083 --> 01:53:49,077
So that the seas may salute you.

1268
01:53:49,155 --> 01:53:52,420
Happy birthday to you.

1269
01:53:52,558 --> 01:53:53,650
You're 18 years old now.

1270
01:53:54,827 --> 01:53:56,556
You've become a man,
which is why I'm giving this to you.

1271
01:53:57,563 --> 01:53:59,155
This was my grandfather's watch.

1272
01:54:01,033 --> 01:54:03,024
He gave it to my father,
who then gave it to me

1273
