The car?

1304
01:58:20,693 --> 01:58:21,751
Buy a new one.

1305
01:58:22,695 --> 01:58:23,753
Where?

1306
01:58:27,900 --> 01:58:29,891
Not him. The car.

1307
02:00:04,129 --> 02:00:05,187
