with my marriage?

1313
02:01:18,604 --> 02:01:21,402
No. Not at all. I'm delighted.

1314
02:01:22,474 --> 02:01:24,066
You will now have someone else to
share your frustrations with,

1315
02:01:24,476 --> 02:01:26,137
and Arjun won't need to
go to the hospital again.

1316
02:01:29,081 --> 02:01:30,139
Excuse me.

1317
02:01:33,552 --> 02:01:34,610
Rohan.

1318
02:01:35,621 --> 02:01:36,883
Rohan.

1319
02:01:58,377 --> 02:01:59,901
You fucker...!

1320
02:04:31,164 --> 02:04:32,222
I'm going to Bombay.

1321
02:04:37,037 --> 02:04:38,095
What will you do there?

1322
02:04:39,773 --> 02:04:41,570
I'll work in Vikram's restaurant.

1323
02:04:43,777 --> 02:04:47,110
I'll write. I'll clean toilets.

1324
02:04:47,647 --> 02:04:49,046
But I won't ever come back.

1325
02:10:05,832 --> 02:10:13,295
Though our feet be chained,
our dreams will always float free.

1326
02:10:15,108 --> 02:10:22,981
Even the tender sprouts break
through the mighty earth.

1327
02:10:24,250 --> 02:10:32,851
Hopeful hearts can hold no fear....

1328
02:10:33,860 --> 02:10:43,861
