Freedom...

1348
02:12:26,973 --> 02:12:36,177
Can never be asked for.

1349
02:12:36,582 --> 02:12:41,383
Freedom...

1350
02:12:41,587 --> 02:12:45,182
Freedom...

1351
02:12:46,259 --> 02:12:55,998
Seize it and live forever free.

1352
02:13:00,740 --> 02:13:05,268
How do you cage someone's thoughts?

1353
02:13:05,411 --> 02:13:10,212
Just as soon as birds grow wings,

1354
02:13:10,349 --> 02:13:15,150
They soar high up in the sky.

1355
02:13:16,022 --> 02:13:18,013
I'm taking Arjun with me.

1356
02:13:18,291 --> 02:13:20,020
If I leave him here he will become

1357
02:13:20,293 --> 02:13:22,090
another version of you.

1358
02:13:22,428 --> 02:13:26,296
One of you is enough for this world.

1359
02:13:27,033 --> 02:13:31,436
You will never understand
why this happened.

1360
02:13:32,171 --> 02:13:38,576
Because it's a word you've
never known or experienced...

1361
02:13:39,512 --> 02:13:40,570
Love.

1362
02:13:41,781 --> 02:13:46,047
Please don't try to find us.
If you come within a 100 kilometers of us,

1363
02:13:46,252 --> 02:13:49,244
the police will know that you beat Arjun.

1364
02:13:49,655 --> 02:13:53,056
Legally, it's a criminal offence.

1365
02:13:54,060 --> 02:13:57,052
Arjun can be a lot
more than just your slave.

1366
02:13:57,396 --> 02:14:00,058
He needs a family, not a cage.

1367
02:14:00,466 --> 02:14:04,527
He needs a future, which I will make
sure he gets, whatever the cost...

1368
02:14:05,204 --> 02:14:09,470
Congratulations on your new wife,
Your new daughter, your new life.

1369
02:14:10,076 --> 02:14:12,135
Your son, Rohan.

1370
02:14:13,145 --> 02:14:22,281
Is life over?
Or has it about to begin?

1371
02:14:23,422 --> 02:14:32,091
Is this nightfall?
Or is it a new dawn?

1372
02:14:32,498 --> 02:14:38,095
Will the future bring comfort?

1373
